ent. In more\nmassive galaxies, the flat relation could be explained by a different SMBH\nfuelling mechanism that is decoupled from the star formation of the host galaxy\n(e.g. hot diffuse gas). Finally, we compare the host galaxy properties of X-ray\nabsorbed and unabsorbed sources. Our results show no difference which suggests\nthat X-ray absorption is not linked with the properties of the galaxy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 20 Jun 2021 11:10:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-05"}
